text: Puerto Rico Highway 253 (PR-253) is a tertiary route located in Culebra, Puerto Rico. It goes from the PR-250 on the drawbridge over the Ensenada Canal and runs east, Playa Sardinas II, towards Fulladosa and Punta Aloe. It extends approximately 3.2 km to the access road to Punta del Soldado. ==Major intersections== ==See also== *List of highways numbered 253 ==References== ==External links== * 253 Category:Culebra, Puerto Rico
